org.springframework.data.gemfire.config.annotation

Class EntityDefinedRegionsConfiguration.RegionBeanDefinitionMetadata

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.data.gemfire.config.annotation.EntityDefinedRegionsConfiguration.RegionBeanDefinitionMetadata
  • Enclosing class:
    EntityDefinedRegionsConfiguration

    protected static class EntityDefinedRegionsConfiguration.RegionBeanDefinitionMetadata
extends java.lang.Object
    The EntityDefinedRegionsConfiguration.RegionBeanDefinitionMetadata class encapsulates details for creating a Region from application persistent entities. The details are captured during a persistent entity component scan.
    See Also:
